12,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fe66a96047b9946a0ecd809c91fc6d89c7983d","tid":1780012,"uid":60830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"高姿態行街，仲要個個商場都咁多人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我點買禮物呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff63d614f2f77c55deefa2fec6e0e460ed239f84","tid":1780012,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4fe66a96047b9946a0ecd809c91fc6d89c7983d","tid":1780012,"uid":60830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"高姿態行街，仲要個個商場都咁多人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我點買禮物呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"佢越高姿態越有利<br />\n曱甴既出現會聚到一班人口遁佢"},{"pid":"b2caae924d1e0f41cd12c9ec5d9215f15f28f8e0","tid":1780012,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb68d44e0dd0a55611ac5045665692adbba1de9","tid":1780012,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac697b7edb1cae661f31ebd446c097c879a8330","tid":1780012,"uid":45466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a206afd26b821284efc3ae0c235c4575453e7570","tid":1780012,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de3629b2f