日子<br />\n而今日到20號期間希望勇武手足能夠好好休息<br />\n由和理非主導<br />\n等到20號打後就係勇武主場 盡情爆發<br />\n曱甴都會開始部署 相信佢地會由中學生放假後會有更多高姿態巡邏<br />\n旺角 尖沙咀 係曱甴高姿態巡邏要點<br />\n亦會部署咗大量便衣<br />\n尋晚已經見到便衣會先拉人 綠色曱甴再出現<br />\n但可以見到便衣約4-5個為一組<br />\n只會針對落單手足 所以小隊建議人數為8-10人 有2個係街坊look報哨睇水<br />\n而我地主要爆發日子當然係24-26號呢3日<br />\n大家可以見到呢排已經多咗好多大陸人落返嚟 佢地主要去大商場消費<br />\n所以和你shop必需繼續做<br />\n而勇武手足建議10區開花 衝衝子可以打流水式陣地 牽制曱甴<br />\n而小隊可以靜靜雞行動<br />\n只要捱過咗聖誕 新年呢個消費旺季<br />\n個市仲係咁差<br />\n攬炒目的已達成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"全球罷買支那貨慶祝聖誕，幫我推到全世界睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784907</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6bfb253db31d7cf49ab5d2f624a2d57dde38645a","tid":1780012,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"推呀 20號就會釋放咗中學手足既行動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e604dbb816ad368dff5042b0ce145259ba84696d","tid":1780012,"uid":101034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abb83d7bd1f8a06ae3f23fc2384707e613d0c3d","tid":1780012,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"和理非日日塞商場 不消費佢都已經大撚獲"},{"pid":"b03fbf4fa0c8fc747d602388e66be4e73a526c1d","tid":1780012,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14011861f90d971b78c55a4dfda6e2a8727c41d6","tid":1780012,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,